properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St. Augustine FL out 20 NM; Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 11 at 2:24AM EST until January 11 at 11:00PM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas 5 to 7 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from Altamaha Sound to Fernandina Beach
FL out 20 NM and Coastal waters from Fernandina Beach to St.
Augustine FL out 20 NM.

* WHEN...Until 11 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 11 PM EST THIS EVENING
